The financial consequences from a state enforced shut-down of a restaurant or business can be devastating and sometimes the doors may never open again. Even when a business can survive the loss of income during a shut-down period, it may never recover from the negative effects of the damage  to its reputation. Serve It Up Safe exists so that such a problem can be prevented.
